  <brief_title>Dose-dependent Effects of Second-hand Smoke on Vascular Function</brief_title>
  <official_title>Dose-dependent Biological Mechanisms of Second-hand Smoke on Endothelial Function and Oxidative Stress</official_title>
  <sponsors>
